    "created_at": "2016-05-04T17:43:35Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-04T17:46:46Z",
    "body": "This is expected behavior as the `BrowserWindow` isn't created instantaneously.\n\nInstead of continuously trying to call `show` you should do the following:\n\n``` js\nconst win = new BrowserWindow()\nwin.webContents.on('did-finish-load', () => {\n    win.show()\n})\n```\n"
